description.narrative: UNICEF Bolivia continued improving the efficiency of joint intervention processes (Partnerships) with governmental and non-governmental entities while strengthening the internal/external capacity to implement programmes and related funding. New tools were developed, and user-friendly support documents and guidelines were designed to ensure timely policy compliance and expenditures.UNICEF Bolivia followed the New Generation of Situation Analysis (SitAn) guidance to prepare two SitAn (Alpha and Beta). Moreover, a Power-Bi Dashboard was created containing information related to the situation of children and adolescents in Bolivia. UNICEF expects both processes will inform current programmatic efforts and the new CPD drafting process. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:07/12/2021
